features: 【Packing List】You will get 24 sheets of vintage style letter paper and 8 vintage envelopes (4 different unique looks), 8 hemp ropes, 8 metal keys (2 styles), 8 small sealing stickers and 4 sealing stickers that can be torn into desired shapes by hand.

【4 Retro Flower Designs】The stationary set is designed with 4 different vintage flower patterns and warm colors, adding vintage metal keys and twine to make the letters full of classical style and make your letters more attractive.

【Thick Paper, Double-Sided Printing】Vintage stationery set are made of 150GSM extra-thick kraft paper, thick and sturdy, smooth writing, not easy to bleed, and not blurry. Stationary writing paper is printed on both sides with different patterns.
【Size Details】Lined vintage paper measures 9.8 x 6.9 in/ 25 x 17.6 cm, stationary envelopes measures 7.3 x 5.1 in/ 18.5 x 13 cm. The length of the hemp rope is 1m/39in.

【Special Vintage Greeting Cards】These vintage floral letter writing set are perfect for writing vintage letters, but also for greeting cards, note cards with envelopes, vintage style wedding invitations, birthday invitations, party invitations, well wishes messages and more.
body.description: Features of Letter Writing Paper and Envelopes Set ◆High-Quality Ink Printing: Natural ink is selected, with thick coloring and clear patterns. ◆Thick Paper: 150g kraft paper, reliable to write, not easy for ink to bleed. ◆How to Pack Antique Paper: Put the old looking paper directly into the envelope or roll it up with twine. ◆Hand-tearable sealing stickers: In addition to using pre-cut envelope stickers, you can also hand-tear the stickers for a more natural effect. ◆Text Embellishment: There are warm text embellishments on the vintage stationary paper to leave a deep impression on your recipients.
